I used to be a member almost 10 years ago. No, this is not me coming back to the game, considering there's barely a game to back to, too.

Back in the day (you can read my replies around page 25, that I've found at least. What am I saying, no one will read this) my English was not perfect. In fact, I had a hard time grasping the world outside my own bubble of a country, or even the area I lived in. So sometimes I said pretty strange stuff. Somehow, CB (many other clans tried too) took me in, even though I wasn't even that great of a player. It was all because I was so active.

Most of the members are fuck-old now, some were already old back when I played. Sometimes I reminisce about this game, and the community I was in... like now.

Sort of sad to see it completely barren, even stripped apart now that browsers don't let you play it, but all things must go. I have spent years not coming back to this game so I'll surely survive without it. And it's not like Motion Twin's current ventures aren't worthwhile.

To be fair don't know what compelled me to write this haha, maybe I just wanted to leave a mark that I am back after a whole decade. I don't know. No one will see it anyway.
